article.description: — Dalton Banks had 15 points in Illinois State's 61-52 victory over Long Beach State on Monday in an opening-round game of the Gulf Coast Showcase.
article.headline: Illinois State wins 61-52 over Long Beach State
article.linkText: Illinois State wins 61-52 over Long Beach State
article.story: ESTERO, Fla. -- — Dalton Banks had 15 points in Illinois State's 61-52 victory over Long Beach State on Monday in an opening-round game of the Gulf Coast Showcase. Banks added five rebounds and six steals for the Redbirds (3-1). Johnny Kinziger was 3 of 7 shooting (2 for 5 from 3-point range) to add 10 points. Messiah Thompson finished with 10 points and four assists for the Beach (2-3). Long Beach State also got eight points, 15 rebounds and two steals from Lassina Traore. AJ George also recorded eight points and six rebounds. Long Beach State was coming off a 94-86 victory over Michigan in its last game. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
